### Phase {{N}} — Publish

Write the artifact to a temp file, then publish via `safer-publish`:

```bash
TMP=$(mktemp)
cat > "$TMP" <<'ARTIFACT'
{{Artifact body — markdown, with the canonical sections this modality emits.}}
ARTIFACT

if [ -n "${SAFER_PARENT_ISSUE:-}" ]; then
  URL=$(safer-publish --kind comment --issue "$SAFER_PARENT_ISSUE" --repo "$REPO" --body-file "$TMP")
else
  URL=$(safer-publish --kind issue --repo "$REPO" --title "{{title template}}" --body-file "$TMP" --labels "safer:{{state-label}}")
fi
echo "Published: $URL"
```

### Phase {{N+1}} — Status

Set the sub-issue label to the next state (`safer:reviewing`, `safer:verifying`, `safer:done`, etc.) via `safer-transition-label`. Update the parent epic's `## Status` block if running under orchestrate.

